Coding assistance: code completion, quick documentation, code refactorings, etc.

code completion (basic)           ctrl + space
code completion (type matching)   ctrl + shift + space

complete current statement        shift + cmd + return

quick definition      opt + space or cmd + Y
quick documentation   ctrl + J
parameter Info        cmd + P
type Info             ctrl + shift + P
show source           cmd + return

next method                     ctrl + shift + arrow down
prev method                     ctrl + shift + arrow up
move caret to matching Brace    ctrl + M
goto declaration or usages      cmd + B
goto implementations            opt + cmd + B
goto type declaration           shift + cmd + B


move statement down   shift + cmd + arrow down
move statement up     shift + cmd + arrow up
move line down        shift + opt + arrow down
move line up          shift + opt + arrow up

multi caret           opt + click

delete line           cmd + delete
duplicate line        cmd + D

extend selection      option + arrow up

start new line          shift + return
start new line before   opt + cmd + return

next parameter    tab
prev parameter    shift + tab

next template variable  return or tab
show options popup      opt + shift + O
